rows.label: qst102103_msg0001
rows.name:
This is the worst. Especially
since you started talking to me.

rows.label: qst102103_msg0003
rows.name: How did the mission go for you?

rows.label: qst102103_msg0004
rows.name:
Are you used to the
mercenary corps yet?

rows.label: qst102103_msg0101
rows.name: I shouldn't have taken this job...

rows.label: qst102103_msg0102
rows.name:
I just want to go home already. What
is that Superbian fool doing...?

rows.label: qst102103_msg0202
rows.name:
There are way too many people
from other countries...

rows.label: qst102103_msg0203
rows.name:
I don't get why so many
of them gather here...

rows.label: qst102103_msg0204
rows.name:
And on top of that, they're all
overly-friendly people like you.
